{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/club-activities/volunteer-firefighters","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"Volunteer firefighters ","meta_description":"Rules and recommendations for volunteer firefighters.","content":{"processed":"<p><strong>Rules and recommendations </strong></p>\n<p>Volunteer firefighters in normal operation must follow all emergency measures at the moment. Exceptions to free movement are activities designed to ensure <strong>security, internal order</strong> or <strong>crisis management</strong>. Typically, these are emergency trips to fires, floods or other disasters. When leaving firefighters must be equipped with <strong>protective equipment that is adapted to the type of intervention.</strong> During all activities it is also necessary, according to the situation, to pay maximum attention to hygienic measures.</p>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/club-activities/volunteer-firefighters"},"changed":"2020-12-02T14:19:48+00:00","valid_from":"2020-11-04T00:00:00+01:00","langcode":"en","created":"2020-11-04T23:57:31+00:00","links":[],"relationships":{"region":[{"name":"All regions of Czechia"}],"icon":{"code":"nature_people"},"situation_type":{"name":"Club activities","path":{"alias":"/situations/club-activities"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"nature_people"}}},"measures":[],"related_situations":[]},"questions_answers":[{"question":"Do I have to wear a face mask in the car during the way to the place of intervention?","value":"Yes."},{"question":"Do I have to have wear a face mask whilst extinguishing the fire?","value":"No."}],"update":null,"valid_to":"2020-11-20T23:59:59+01:00","last_updated":"2020-12-01T16:26:27+01:00"},"situationArea":{"name":"Club activities","path":{"alias":"/situations/club-activities"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"nature_people"},"situation":[{"id":"ae1aed24-d6ad-5481-be68-d8d9c9bac49f","title":"Volunteer firefighters ","path":{"alias":"/situations/clu